<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
  <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#84CC16]">
    Privacy Policy
  </h1>

  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-6">
    <p class="text-white">Last updated: July 21, 2025</p>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        Introduction
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        Welcome to Chrima. We take your privacy seriously, which is why
        we've designed our app to keep your data completely private and
        under your control. All your data is stored locally on your device -
        we don't collect, track, or have access to any of your personal or
        financial information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        Local Data Storage
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        When you use Chrima, all your data is stored exclusively on your
        device:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-400">
        <li>Expense records and categories</li>
        <li>Subscription information</li>
        <li>App preferences and settings</li>
        <li>Any financial data you input</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4">
        We do not have servers storing your data - everything stays on your
        device, giving you complete control over your information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        No Data Collection or Tracking
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        We believe in privacy by design. Therefore:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-400">
        <li>No user authentication or account creation required</li>
        <li>No analytics or usage tracking</li>
        <li>No data transmission to external servers</li>
        <li>No advertising or marketing data collection</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        Your Data Control
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">You have complete control over your data:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-400">
        <li>Export your data anytime in common formats</li>
        <li>Delete your data directly from your device</li>
        <li>
          Back up your data using your device's built-in backup features
        </li>
        <li>No cloud sync - your data stays on your device</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        App Permissions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        Chrima only requests essential device permissions needed for basic
        app functionality. We don't access any sensitive device features or
        information beyond what's necessary for the app to work on your
        device.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        Data Security
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        Since all data is stored locally on your device, its security
        depends on your device's security settings. We recommend:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-400">
        <li>Keeping your device's operating system updated</li>
        <li>
          Using device security features (password/biometric protection)
        </li>
        <li>Regularly backing up your device</li>
        <li>
          Being mindful of apps that have access to your device's storage
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        Contact Us
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        If you have any questions about our privacy practices or how we
        handle your data, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p class="text-white">Email: privacy@chrima.app</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#84CC16]">
        Changes to This Policy
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect
        changes in our app's functionality or applicable privacy laws. Any
        updates will be posted on this page with a new "Last updated" date.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</div> 